== Guides & Documentation

Key resources to support mentors, podlings, and the Incubator PMC. These guides cover onboarding, mentoring practices, governance, reporting, and lessons learned.

=== Getting Started / Orientation
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Incubator+Mentor+Quick+Start+Guide[Mentor Quick Start Guide] — fast orientation for new mentors  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Mentor+Onboarding[Mentor Onboarding] — step-by-step entry into mentoring  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Incubator+PMC+Onboarding[Incubator PMC Onboarding] — orientation for joining the IPMC  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Podling+Committer+Onboarding[Podling Committer Onboarding] — what new committers need to know  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Podling+PPMC+Onboarding[Podling PPMC Onboarding] — duties of the PPMC  

=== Practical Tools & Guidance
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Mentor+Quick+Reference+-+Common+Red+Flags[Common Red Flags] — warning signs to watch for  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Best+Practices+for+Mentors[Best Practices for Mentors] — 50 practical mentoring scenarios  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Mentors+Tough+Conversation+Guide[Mentors Tough Conversation Guide] — handling difficult discussions  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/TRAINING/ASF+Project+Reporting+Guidance[Project Report Guide] — how to prepare IPMC/podling reports  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/International+and+Cultural+Awareness[International & Cultural Awareness] — guidance for inclusive global collaboration  

=== Governance & Compliance
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Selecting+a+PMC+Chair[Selecting a PMC Chair] — process and considerations  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Third-Party+Branding+and++Incubating+Projects[Third-Party Branding & Incubating Projects] — rules for names/branding  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Podling+Path%3A+Governance+in+Practice[Governance in Practice] — practical ASF values and decision-making  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/How+to+Use+the+ASF+Maturity+Model[How To Use the ASF Maturity Model] — assessing project readiness  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATORVendor+Neutrality[Vendor Neutrality] — principles for avoiding domination by any one vendor  

=== Learning from Experience
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Incubator+Case+Studies[Incubator Case Studies] — successes and challenges of past podlings  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Incubation+Explained%3A+Purpose%2C+Practice%2C+and+Lessons+Learned[Incubation Explained] — overview of the Incubator’s purpose, practices, and lessons learned  

=== Lifecycle & Transitions
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Podling+Orientation+Guide[Podling Orientation Guide] — introduction & expectations for new podlings  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Graduation+and+Beyond[Graduation & Beyond] — post-graduation transition and ongoing relationship  
- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Mentor+Offboarding[Mentor Offboarding] — stepping back at graduation or retirement  